	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Are there any tutorials or information on NESICIDE version 1 (I prefer this version, but I can use v2 if I have to)? I have been searching for days on how to use these things, but can't find anything. Can anyone here point me to some tutorials or just general information on this? It looks like quite a powerful tool.
<br />
<br />Also, some 6502 ABSOLUTE BEGINNER tutorials (specifically for the NES) would be helpful. All the tutorials that I've read seem to assume you know everything about how a computer/NES works... I've been working with C/C++ for a while and it's been hard to grasp the concepts (e.g. I just learned what data registers were yesterday).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
