		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />No idea about NESICIDE.
<br />
<br />For beginner info on how the 6502 works, I like this guide: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdev.com/6502guid.txt">http://nesdev.com/6502guid.txt</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />For a beginner's guide to NES programming, read the nerdy nights tutorials (It will probably be more of what you want than the other guide: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.nintendoage.com/forum/messageview.cfm?catid=22&amp;threadid=7155">http://www.nintendoage.com/forum/messag ... eadid=7155</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />Edit: And if you have specific questions about the concepts you don't grasp, post them as well.

		

