	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">keelx wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Are there any tutorials or information on NESICIDE version 1 (I prefer this version, but I can use v2 if I have to)? </div>
<br />
<br />What is it about NESICIDE 1 that you prefer?  Given a list I might consider bumping those up in priority and start porting them to NESICIDE 2.  I am not maintaining NESICIDE 1 anymore...I don't have VS 6 installed and it doesn't want to install in Win7 anyway.  I need a good push in the porting direction...motivation is low there!
<br />
<br />The assembler in NESICIDE 1 isn't one of the mainstream assemblers that people here will help you with.  It was a "roll your own" attempt I made but have since abandoned.
<br />
<br />There aren't any tutorials for NESICIDE 1 but <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/nesicideproject/documents" class="postlink">here</a> are various example projects based on ROMs [all of them top notch, if you ask me!] developed by people that frequent this board.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


